INSERT INTO superhero VALUES (171,'1516608605-6186','Data','https://www.superherodb.com/data/10-10577/',100,35,25,40,60,50,'-','No alter egos found.','B-4','-','-','Star Trek','good','Male','Android','- // 0 cm','- lb // 0 kg','Yellow','Brown','Lieutenant commander','-','Starfleet,Federation','Dr. Noonian Soong (creator)','Data''s history','https://www.superherodb.com/data/10-10577/history/','On February 2nd, 2338, Data was discovered by the crew of the U.S.S. Tripoli, a Federation ship that responded to a distress call sent from Omicron Theta. They reactivated Data, and Data attempted to join Starfleet as a show of gratitude. He was admitted into the Academy in 2341. Data graduated the Academy in 2345 with honors in Exobiology and probability mechanics.','','','','','','','','/pictures2/portraits/10/100/10577.jpg');
