INSERT INTO superhero VALUES (645,'1516610312-8062','Ajax','https://www.superherodb.com/ajax/10-10422/',60,50,35,80,35,55,'Francis','No alter egos found.','\"Frankie\", the A-Man, the Attending','-','Deadpool #14 (March, 1998)','Marvel Comics','bad','Male','Cyborg','6''4 // 193 cm','200 lb // 90 kg','Brown','Black','-','-','','-','Ajax''s history','https://www.superherodb.com/ajax/10-10422/history/','The man known only as Francis was the former enforcer at Doctor Killebrew''s laboratory, known as the Workshop, part of the Hospice for failed supersoldiers at the Weapon X Project. Francis acted as the strongarm for Killebrew, reigning in the project''s \"washouts\" that were fodder for Killebrew''s sadistic experiments whenever they stepped out of line. This included one Wade Wilson.','','','','','','','','/pictures2/portraits/10/100/10422.jpg');
