INSERT INTO superhero VALUES (678,'1516608928-6531','Cheetah II','https://www.superherodb.com/cheetah-ii/10-925/',40,20,45,20,40,60,'Deborah Domaine','No alter egos found.','Debbi, The Cheetah','-','Wonder Woman Vol1 #274 (Dec 1980)','DC Comics','bad','Female','Human','5''7 // 170 cm','122 lb // 55 kg','Green','Brown','-','Chesapeake Bay, Maryland','Secret Society of Super-Villains,Cheetah','Priscilla Rich (Cheetah I, aunt), Claudia Rich (aunt)','','','','Cheetah II''s powers','https://www.superherodb.com/cheetah-ii/10-925/powers/','[{\"powers\":\"Since her transformation, Debbi was never seen without her Cheetah costume and ears. She was a superb athlete with cat-like grace and a great hand-to-hand combatant. When enraged, her strength became almost superhuman. This, combined with the razor-sharp fingernails she possessed, capable of cutting through solid steel, made Debbi a formidable foe.\"}]','','','','','/pictures2/portraits/10/100/925.jpg');
INSERT INTO superhero VALUES (679,'1516607876-5035','Gravity','https://www.superherodb.com/gravity/10-74/',50,35,35,40,70,30,'Greg Willis','No alter egos found.','Protector of the Universe','Sheboygan, Wisconsin','Gravity #1 (August, 2005)','Marvel Comics','good','Male','Human','5''10 // 178 cm','175 lb // 79 kg','Blue','Brown','Student','New York City','','Richard Willis (father), Mary Willis (mother)','Gravity''s history','https://www.superherodb.com/gravity/10-74/history/','Other people in Willis'' life included \"Frog,\" his roommate, and Lauren Singh, another student.\nGravity was one of the heroes taken to Battleworld, along with Spider-Man (Impostor), Medusa, Wasp, Firebird, Venom and Henry Pym by a being claiming to be the Beyonder. Later, when Uatu the Watcher appeared, the ''Beyonder'' was proven to be a hoax, It ended up being another cosmic entity known as The Stranger. The being then decided to destroy the planet, setting it to self destruct. Gravity forfeited his life to hold it together long enough for the others to escape.','','','','','','','','/pictures2/portraits/10/100/74.jpg');
