INSERT INTO superhero VALUES (801,'1516605347-1787','Sentry','https://www.superherodb.com/sentry/10-447/',75,100,100,85,100,40,'Robert Reynolds','Death Seed Sentry','Void, Bob, Golden Guardian of Good, John Victor Williams, Scout','-','Sentry #1 (September, 2000)','Marvel Comics','neutral','Male','Mutant','6''2 // 188 cm','194 lb // 87 kg','Blue','Blond','-','The Watchtower (on top of Stark Tower, where it was formerly located before all memory of him disappeared)','Dark Avengers,Apocalypse''s Horsemen,Super Soldiers,Horsemen of Apocalypse,New Warriors,New Avengers,Avengers,Gods','Lindy Reynolds (wife, deceased), Mrs. Reynolds (mother)','Sentry''s history','https://www.superherodb.com/sentry/10-447/history/','The Sentry then visited Dr. Strange to determine if he was real or not. Strange tricked the Sentry into traveling to his old Professor''s research facility where the two men confined the Sentry in an illusionary realm where he was a mental patient and superheroes didn''t exist in an attempt to prevent any further destruction. The Sentry broke free of the illusion and after confronting the Professor who made the original serum, he traveled to Antarctica to confront the Void and discover what memories of Reynolds the Void has in his mind.','','','','','','','','/pictures2/portraits/10/100/447.jpg');
